JACQUE FRESCO:
==============
You may also pay attention to interesting ideas of Jacque Fresco.  About 50 millions of people today are know about his project &quot;The Venus Project&quot;. This project is far not only about technology (as some people might think at first glance). Fresco try to exaplain to people about what shapes human behaviour, hwo environment makes one's life values. I think that A. S. Neill had even deeper understanding of our todays problems than Fresco. But however it is very useful to pay attention too. By the way, Fresco is born in 1916, and still gives a lectures.

